Package it.polimi.ingsw.server.model.developmentcard

Class DevelopmentCard

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.server.model.developmentcard.DevelopmentCard
All Implemented Interfaces:
VictoryPointsElement
public class DevelopmentCard
extends java.lang.Object
implements VictoryPointsElement
Card which can be placed in development card slots and used to convert the required input resource into the fixed output resources. When activating a production, its outputs will be stored in the player's strongbox.
